{"title":"巴山春歌","authors":["艾莹"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山春歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山风雨来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨浓山影淡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看巴山啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向雨抽笋鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎雷开杜鹃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花水涨千条堰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗绿了万层田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梨花云湿听布谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳陌绿看紫燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花开淋雨起火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆飞乘风过千山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山人去来灵如燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披蓑戴笠悠悠然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支小曲翻过山："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农械厂里催农机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘山沿水查渠堰……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社大点兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人喊马嘶，张弓紧弦——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选种歌满屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"檐下试新鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声拥着决心书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天贴到支书窗子前……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山的春天啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风里雨里来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨催春春烂漫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山的春天啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风里雨里来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来得步步鲜花红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来得步步雷响电闪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山山水巴山人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有过光荣的风雨战斗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山的春天啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风里雨里来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来得风阻雨拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来得泥泞艰难……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山山水巴山人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里夺春天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨涨的是潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风推动是帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨洗江山新更新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风展红旗春万年！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}